                  <path d="M18.5 17.5C20 16 22 16 23.5 17.5" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  <path d="M18.5 22.5C20 24 22 24 23.5 22.5" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Sex / Mating Pheromones</h4>
              <p>
                Released by one sex to attract mates, often over <strong>enormous distances</strong>
                (kilometres in some moth species). Highly species-specific — the precise ratio of
                chemical components prevents cross-species attraction.
              </p>
              <span class="pheromone-type-badge pheromone-type-badge--releaser">Releaser</span>
            </div>

